nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Ryan-Gosling-Margot-Robbie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>芭比娃娃</em></a>编剧<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/greta-gerwig-fight-keep-im-just-ken-sequence-barbie-3511938">格蕾塔·葛韦格</a>和诺亚·鲍姆巴赫分享了玩具制造公司美泰在剧本中给出的一些注释。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/barbie-review-margot-robbie-ryan-gosling-3470019">《芭比娃娃》评论：格蕾塔·葛韦格的成人玩具故事非常有趣</a></strong></li></ul><p>这对电影制作夫妻最近与作家托尼·库什纳一起庆祝这部破纪录的大片。据<a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/barbie-mattel-script-notes-execs-shot-1235779179/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>报道，他们透露，在电影中肯斯之间的海滩战斗场景中，首席执行官威尔·法雷尔 (Will Ferrell) 领导的美泰高管被假箭射中。</p><p>鲍姆巴赫（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/marriage-story-review-noah-baumbach-2554638"><em>《婚姻故事》</em></a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/white-noise-review-noah-baumbach-netflix-3359778"><em>《白噪音</em></a>》）说：“我们第一次翻剧本时有一个注释。第 111 页：“美泰高管必须被枪杀吗？”当时我们就想，这应该出现在广告上！” </p><figure id="attachment_3532167" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3532167" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3532167" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baumbach-and-Gerwig.jpg" alt="诺亚·鲍姆巴赫和格蕾塔·葛韦格" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baumbach-and-Gerwig.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baumbach-and-Gerwig-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baumbach-and-Gerwig-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baumbach-and-Gerwig-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baumbach-and-Gerwig-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Baumbach-and-Gerwig-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3532167" class="wp-caption-text">诺亚·鲍姆巴赫 (Noah Baumbach) 和格蕾塔·葛韦格 (Greta Gerwig) 于 2020 年 2 月 1 日在纽约。图片来源：Getty/摄影：Dominik Bindl/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>但葛韦格对美泰的注释进行了权衡，并补充说这些注释是暗示性的，而不是严格的。她补充道，“所有笔记的末尾都有一个问号。这并不是说，“这必须发生。”更多的是，‘但他必须如此吗？’”</p><p>这部电影高度讽刺并偶尔批评美泰公司的大规模生产、男性领导的管理委员会以及通过芭比娃娃塑造的女性形象，票房收入超过 14 亿美元。据<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-67223711" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC 报道</em></a>，这部电影的成功也影响了美泰公司的业绩，7 月至 9 月期间<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/success-of-barbie-film-leads-to-major-spike-in-the-toys-sales-3524134">芭比玩具的销量比去年增长了 16%</a> 。</p><p> But this wasn&#39;t the first time the filmmakers had to override one of Mattel&#39;s suggestions. According to <a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/mattel-ceo-argued-margot-robbie-barbie-scene-off-brand-1235655398/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a> , it was revealed on the film&#39;s press tour that Gerwig and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/margot-robbie">Margot Robbie</a> had to convince Mattel President and COO, Richard Dickson, to keep in the scene featuring the character, Sasha, criticising Barbie.</p><p> However, Gerwig added that Mattel CEO <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/barbie-heres-whos-on-the-real-life-mattel-board-3473199">Ynon Kreiz,</a> “really did give us a tremendous amount of trust and freedom. There was a real, &#39;If you say this is right, then let&#39;s go.&#39;”</p><p> In other news, Gerwig said that this <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/barbie-star-should-play-next-james-bond-says-greta-gerwig-3530213"><em>Barbie</em> star should be the next James Bond.</a></p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/barbie-mattel-beach-executive-3532147">Mattel didn&#39;t want their executive to get shot in &#39;Barbie&#39; beach scene</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
